### EnergyController requests for IntelliJ HTTP Client
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Get current energy data
GET {{baseUrl}}/energy/current
Accept: application/json

### Get historic energy data
# Use ISO-8601 local date-time values (no timezone), and keep start < end.
GET {{baseUrl}}/energy/historic?start=2026-04-29T10:00:00&end=2026-04-29T12:00:00
Accept: application/json

